  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">7 Updating and Control of Your Personal Information We offer you choices regarding the collection use and sharing of your Personal Information When you receive promotional communications from us you will have the opportunity to opt-out by following the unsubscribe instructions provided in the promotional e-mail or newsletter you receive or by editing your preference to receive these communications within the Manage My Email or similar feature on the individual Sites when you are logged in as a registered user</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

