<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="#d0f1d02435e54a328eec076:Encryption">
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#Encryption"/>
  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">d0f1d02435e54a328eec076</uuid>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">10 Security We place a priority on the security of Personal Information and we undertake reasonable security measures to help protect the data that resides on our servers We also use secure server software SSL to process all financial transactions that occur on the Site SSL technology can encrypt Personal Information transmitted over the Internet However no security system is impenetrable We do not warrant the security of our servers nor do we warrant that your information including Personal Information will be completely secure or not be intercepted while being transmitted over the Internet</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

